text: Joshua Hassall (November 1871 – 1895) was an English footballer who played in the Football League for Wolverhampton Wanderers. ==References== Category:1871 births Category:1895 deaths Category:English footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:English Football League players Category:Birmingham St George's F.C. players Category:Stafford Rangers F.C. players Category:Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C. players
